    "Html": "<p>Hey guys!</p>\r\n<p>I finally managed to get the graph visualized in Windows Forms, but now I was wondering if I coud add events to the graphical representation, like for example, that when I clicl a vertex, a messagebox pops up. How should I apporach this, since the Graph object doesnt seem to have event handling?</p>",
