    "Html": "<p>Hello,</p>\r\n<p>i would like to do nearly the same thing, i.e. showing a contextual menu when right-clicking a vertex.</p>\r\n<p>I use a simple&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\">BidirectionalGraph</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">string</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">, </span><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\">IEdge</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">string</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">&gt;&gt; but i can't figure out what to put in my datatemplate's datatype.</span></p>\r\n<p>I've tried the following:</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">DataTemplate</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"> DataType</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">=&quot;{</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">x</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">:</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">Type</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"> QuickGraph</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">:</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\">TVertex</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">}&quot;&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">&lt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">TextBlock</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"> MouseRightButtonDown</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">=&quot;MouseRightClick&quot;/&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">&lt;/</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">DataTemplate</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">and:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">&lt;DataTemplate</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"> DataType</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">=&quot;String</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">&quot;&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">but these don't work.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">How can I do that?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">thanks.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
